'''Ursu n ureɣ brand''' (''Goldener Bärenmarke'') neɣ '''Ursu n ureɣ n usaru ugaren wiyaḍ nniḍen''' (''Goldener Bär für den besten Langfilm'') d arraz n cciɛa ugaren wiyaḍ nniḍen yettunefken deg [[Taberlinit|Tafaska n Berlin]] seg [[1951]]. Yettunefk sɣur amgalaw unṣib i asaru aɣezfan n timenyagert tagraɣlant. Ursu d azamul n tamdint n Berlin. 

Ursu n ureɣ yetsreɣɣet sɣur [[Renée Sintenis]]. 

Ar ass agi, ala imseḍru ataywani [[Ang Lee]] i rebḥen ursu n ureɣ snat tikkwal (deg 1993 d 1996).


